[Course_Description]
Brightspace is a highly customizable learning management system (LMS) from D2l (Desire2Learn), which helps instructors manage higher education. It offers a flexible UI and supports blended classrooms and online learning. In this course, find out how easy it is to get started. Join instructor Alan Ackmann as he explores essential features and best practices you need to know to teach with Brightspace. Learn how to customize the Brightspace interface, communicate with students, assign and grade student work, and understand how Brightspace functions from the student perspective. Plus, see how to add quizzes, customize the Brightspace experience to improve accessibility for all users, and enhance the community and collaboration in your classroom with tools like discussion boards and feedback. Along the way, Alan shares tips that can help you work more efficiently and effectively with this powerful LMS.